<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="describe-vt">describe <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'skraɪb/    美 /dɪ'skraɪb/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>描述；叙述；形容：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Words cannot describe my joy. 
我的快乐难以言表。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>describe sb / sth to / for sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can you describe her to me?
你能和我描述一下她是什么样子吗？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>describe sb / sth as：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His friends describe Jim as an “angry young man”.
吉姆的朋友说他是个“愤青”。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>describe + wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s difficult to describe how I felt.
很难形容我那时的感受。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>descriptive /dɪ'skrɪptɪv/ adj   </p></div>